# Cursor rules for this repo

## Imports
- Prefer absolute imports via aliases.
  - Use @/… for anything under app/.
  - Use @gen/sanity for generated Sanity query types (type-only imports).
  - Use @root/… for runtime imports from repo root when needed.
- Do not introduce relative imports (../../ etc) except:
  - React Router route type imports must remain ./+types/*.

## Styling
- Tailwind classes only.
- Do not add CSS modules or component-level CSS files.
- Keep global CSS limited to app/app.css (Tailwind v4 @theme tokens + minimal base).

## Structure
- UI primitives go in app/components/ui.
- Feature components go in app/components/features/<feature>.
- Sanity schema-mapped components live in app/components/features/sanity.

## Workflow
- After schema or GROQ changes run pnpm typecheck.
- Format with pnpm format.
